                            </StackLayout>

                            <StackLayout Orientation="Horizontal" Margin="30,0,30,10" Spacing="45">
                                <Label Text="Filming &#10;locations" FontAttributes="Bold" TextColor="Black" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                                <Label Text="Tybee Island, Georgia, USA" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                            </StackLayout>

                            <StackLayout Orientation="Horizontal" Margin="30,0,30,10" Spacing="60">
                                <Label Text="Budget" FontAttributes="Bold" TextColor="Black" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                                <Label Text="$20 million" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                            </StackLayout>

                            <StackLayout Orientation="Horizontal" Margin="30,0,30,15" Spacing="38">
                                <Label Text="Box office" FontAttributes="Bold" TextColor="Black" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                                <Label Text="$89 million" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                            </StackLayout>

                            <Line X1="330"
                                  Y1="0"
                                  Stroke="Gray"
                                  Margin="30,0,30,15"/>

                            <!-- Reviews -->
                            <StackLayout Margin="30,0,10,20">

                                <Label Text="REVIEWS &#10;" FontSize="22" FontAttributes="Bold" TextColor="Black"/>
                                <Label Text="Audience rating summary" HorizontalOptions="CenterAndExpand" FontSize="18" TextColor="Black" CharacterSpacing="0.2" FontAttributes="Bold"/>
                                <Label Text="4.5" HorizontalOptions="CenterAndExpand" FontSize="35"/>
                                <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/P4qVVL3/4-5-stars-2.png" WidthRequest="100"/>
                                <Line X1="330"
                                      Y1="0"
                                      Stroke="Gray"
                                      Margin="50,10,50,10"/>
                                <Label Text="Google users" HorizontalOptions="CenterAndExpand" FontSize="18" TextColor="Black" CharacterSpacing="0.2" FontAttributes="Bold"/>
                                <Label Text="80% liked this film" HorizontalOptions="CenterAndExpand" FontSize="22"/>
                                <Line X1="330"
                                      Y1="0"
                                      Stroke="Gray"
                                      Margin="50,10,50,10"/>
                                <Label Text="Review-aggregation websites&#10;" HorizontalOptions="CenterAndExpand" FontSize="18" TextColor="Black" CharacterSpacing="0.2" FontAttributes="Bold"/>
                                <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/TLN9W92/The-Last-Song2.png" HeightRequest="250"/>

                            </StackLayout>

                            <Line X1="330"
                                  Y1="0"
                                  Stroke="Gray"
                                  Margin="30,0,30,15"/>

                            <!-- Our personal review -->
                            <StackLayout Margin="30,5,10,20" Spacing="15">

                                <Label Text="OUR PERSONAL REVIEW &#10;" FontSize="22" FontAttributes="Bold" TextColor="Black"/>

                                <StackLayout Orientation="Horizontal" Spacing="10">
                                    <Image Source="https://d338t8kmirgyke.cloudfront.net/icons/icon_pngs/000/004/499/original/good.png" HeightRequest="40"/>
                                    <Label Text="This is a really gorgeous movie with beautiful story and amazing actors and it's based on 2009 novel by American author Nicholas Sparks."  TextColor="DarkBlue" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                                </StackLayout>

                                <StackLayout Orientation="Horizontal" Spacing="10">
                                    <Image Source="https://d338t8kmirgyke.cloudfront.net/icons/icon_pngs/000/004/499/original/good.png" HeightRequest="40"/>
                                    <Label Text="We personally really enjoyed this movie, it's so light to watch ... but we warn you ... it's super emotional, at least for us." TextColor="DarkBlue" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.5" />
                                </StackLayout>

                                <StackLayout Orientation="Horizontal" Spacing="10">
                                    <Image Source="https://d338t8kmirgyke.cloudfront.net/icons/icon_pngs/000/004/499/original/good.png" HeightRequest="40"/>
                                    <Label Text="Yes, it's different from the book, but that doesn't mean this movie is bad, in fact it's actually underrated. We don't agree with 'Rotten Tomatoes' and 'Common Sense Media' review at all, we suggest you to watch a movie for yourself and decide."  TextColor="DarkBlue" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                                </StackLayout>

                                <StackLayout Orientation="Horizontal" Spacing="10">
                                    <Image Source="https://d338t8kmirgyke.cloudfront.net/icons/icon_pngs/000/004/499/original/good.png" HeightRequest="40"/>
                                    <Label Text="We think it's worth watching because story is just so beautiful and emotional, and if you're into this kind of movies you'll probablly like it."  TextColor="DarkBlue" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                                </StackLayout>
                                <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/P4qVVL3/4-5-stars-2.png" HeightRequest="30"/>

                            </StackLayout>

                            <Line X1="330"
                                  Y1="0"
                                  Stroke="Gray"
                                  Margin="30,0,30,15"/>

                            <!-- Audience reviews -->
                            <StackLayout Margin="30,5,10,10">

                                <Label Text="AUDIENCE REVIEWS &#10;" FontSize="22" FontAttributes="Bold" TextColor="Black"/>

                                <StackLayout Orientation="Horizontal" Spacing="10">
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/HTKDnKz/person-icon.png"
                                           HeightRequest="40"/>
                                    <Label Text="MENTAL HEALTH &#10;11 months ago   " FontAttributes="Bold" TextColor="Black" FontSize="13" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/Bs7bnky/5.png" WidthRequest="70"/>
                                </StackLayout>
                                <Label Text="This is an underrated movie. Greg Kinnear has done a fab job and Liam was cuter than cute the entire time we saw him on screen. A very heart warming story, with great scenery I think this film is a real good family time.&#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

                                <StackLayout Orientation="Horizontal" Spacing="10">
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/HTKDnKz/person-icon.png"
                                           HeightRequest="40"/>
                                    <Label Text="Cynthia Flanagan &#10;a year ago" FontAttributes="Bold" TextColor="Black" FontSize="13" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/Bs7bnky/5.png" WidthRequest="70"/>
                                </StackLayout>
                                <Label Text="This was a heart warming and very sad movie. Its a great life happening and this does occur. &#10;The acting is superb and so true to life occurrence. &#10;Drama at its best! &#10;I highly recommend it, you will not be sorry.&#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

                                <StackLayout Orientation="Horizontal" Spacing="10">
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/HTKDnKz/person-icon.png"
                                           HeightRequest="40"/>
                                    <Label Text="Shaina Ramos &#10;a year ago" FontAttributes="Bold" TextColor="Black" FontSize="13" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/5v61tGY/3-stars.png" WidthRequest="70"/>
                                </StackLayout>
                                <Label Text="Well this happens everytime they make movies from novels; but whoever read the book before the movie, they've missed a lot of happenings that I would've loved to have seen in the movie. I felt like if they did have the time to put it what they had in the book, the movie would've rated even better! Nonetheless, I wouldn't have wanted to change any of the characters! They played beautiful especially Greg and Miley.&#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

                                <StackLayout Orientation="Horizontal" Spacing="10">
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/HTKDnKz/person-icon.png" HeightRequest="40"/>
                                    <Label Text="Abigail Johnson &#10;3 years ago" FontAttributes="Bold" TextColor="Black" FontSize="13" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/Bs7bnky/5.png" WidthRequest="70"/>
                                </StackLayout>
                                <Label Text="I want to say this movie is the greatest thing that has ever happened to me. Liam Hemsworth is so beautiful and Miley omg. I love them so much. The music, the love, the everything. 10\10 &#10;Lastly, the way he looks at her.&#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

                                <StackLayout Orientation="Horizontal" Spacing="1">
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/HTKDnKz/person-icon.png"
                                           HeightRequest="40"/>
                                    <Label Text="Lindsey June &#10;a year ago" FontAttributes="Bold" TextColor="Black" FontSize="13" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/5v61tGY/3-stars.png" WidthRequest="70"/>
                                </StackLayout>
                                <Label Text="It's okay, I guess. Cyrus' character 'Ronnie' is a bit annoying and dramatic (but I think that's Cyrus' acting). It got to the point where I had to turn it off because I didn't care about seeing her mad all the time. &#10;Otherwise, it's a good movie! Really cute!&#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

                                <StackLayout Orientation="Horizontal" Spacing="10">
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/HTKDnKz/person-icon.png" HeightRequest="40"/>
                                    <Label Text="Zanniyah Rosado &#10;a year ago " FontAttributes="Bold" TextColor="Black" FontSize="13" CharacterSpacing="0.5"/>
                                    <Image Source="https://i.ibb.co/Bs7bnky/5.png" WidthRequest="70"/>
                                </StackLayout>
                                <Label Text="I loved this movie. But one thing for sure is that i have no words for it. All i can say is that can put myself in her shoes because i have been in that situation. I cried and even right now i am still crying.&#10;" TextColor="#37383b" FontSize="15" CharacterSpacing="0.2" />

